configuration interface.

3.7 Licensee shall NOT use the Software's design, user interface, user
experience, workflows, iconography, naming conventions, or any other
aesthetic or conceptual elements as the basis for any independently
developed product.

3.8 Licensee shall NOT add, remove, or modify any branding, copyright
